Requires:
~~~~~~~~~
-
New features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Basic stack elements can now hold additional data.
- Added transition and state behaviours to edit a stack.
- Added hierarchical stack method to get insert levels.
- Stack definition can now set roles that can manage the stack.
- Stack definition can now set render method to be used by stack.
Bug fixes:
~~~~~~~~~~
- Import of workflow stack definition view/edit stack element guards was not
  effective.
New internal features:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
- Stacks now have an edit api, the replace method has been removed.
- manager_stack_ids property on stack definition now defines stacks whose
  managers can manage current stack (not anymore stacks manageable by current
  stack managers)
